media:group.media:title: Creation Calls Cover
media:group.media:description:
This is a cover of Creation Calls by Brian Doerksen.

I actually did this for a homework assignment, and was a bit rushed.  As such, the quality is not as good as I would like.  I've also switched operating systems since my last video and had to switch to a different video editor.  For some reason, no matter how much I tried, I couldn't quite get the audio and video to sync up.  Oh well.
